# AUDIO::GET_PLAYER_RADIO_STATION_INDEX

## Summary
Gets the index of the current players radio station

## Returns
* **INT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns 255 (radio off index) if the function fails.
